ROADMAP

ACTIVATIONS

Strap yourselves in for a journey beyond the realms of time. We’ve set up a few checkpoints for Bouquet to attain immortality. Once we hit a target through percentage, our project will move up several notches.

0% | GRAND LAUNCH

The private discord channel goes live exclusively for CryptoBear Watch Club members. Members gain access to the club as well as global watch influencers and traders.

20% | RAFFLE PRIZES

The first 1,000 mints are awarded limited-edition CryptoBear airdrops which qualifies them for a raffle to win a win a limited-edition watch worth USD 60,000.
The 1001 to 5000th mints also qualify for a raffle to win a limited-edition watch worth USD 60,000.
Upon minting the entire collection, a third limited-edition watch worth USD 60,000 will be up for grabs via the raffle.
The watches will be shipped to winners wherever they may be!

60% | CBWC TOKEN

We're halfway there! At this point, a Crypto token dedicated to collecting luxury NFTs is launched. The token can be used to purchase new collections as well as real watches from the club.

80% | ENTER THE METAVERSE

CryptoBear Watch Club is officially launched in the Metaverse through partnerships with Sandbox and Decentraland. We will feature galleries to display your NFTs as well as games to play and earn CryptoBear Watch Club tokens.

100% | THE NEXT SAGA

Members who hold their NFTs will be awarded rare airdrops as well as limited-edition watches, not only in the Metaverse, but also for real! We are aiming to partner with major brands to grant members exclusive rights to new releases and events in the watch world.
) }
